---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold text-floof-dark">Privacy Policy</h1><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-floof-dark/50">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-floof-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
      <section><h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-floof-dark">What We Collect</h2><p>When you place an order, we collect your name, email, shipping address, and payment info. We also use cookies to improve your browsing experience.</p></section>
      <section><h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-floof-dark">How We Use It</h2><p>Your info is used to process orders, send shipping updates, and occasionally let you know about new drops (only if you opt in). We don't sell your data.</p></section>
      <section><h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-floof-dark">Payment Processing</h2><p>Payments are handled by Stripe. We never see or store your full credit card number.</p></section>
      <section><h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-floof-dark">Fulfillment</h2><p>Orders are fulfilled through Printful. Your shipping info is shared with them solely to deliver your order.</p></section>
      <section><h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-floof-dark">Contact</h2><p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@floof.space" class="text-floof-pink hover:underline">hello@floof.space</a>.</p></section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>